author: USA TODAY
title: Same dress alert: Faith Hill and Carrie Underwood are twinning at the Grammys
text:
Same dress alert: Faith Hill and Carrie Underwood are twinning at the Grammys Cara Kelly , USA TODAY 7:33 p.m. ET Feb. 12, 2017 
Carrie Underwood and Faith Hill had an epic same dress showdown at the Grammys Sunday night. Is Carrie Underwood or Faith Hill gonna Insta the "LOL I can't believe we both wore this dress" photo first? #TheGrammys pic.twitter.com/gBxkTLZd3V — Jarett Wieselman (@JarettSays) February 12, 2017 
We haven't seen so much matching red since the Golden Globes in 2014 – when Amy Adams and Lupita Nyong'o hit the carpet in caped gowns of the same hue, one Adams quickly shrugged off and didn't put back on for the rest of the evening. 
Unfortunately, neither of these ladies could take off any parts of their long sleeved gowns with diamond-shaped cut
